Class ParkDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.ParkDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ParkDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents the details of a park, including the name of the park manager, park name, time of stay, difference, and maximum number of visitors allowed.
